## ðŸ“Š Evaluation Logic

Candilyzer uses no assumptions and follows strict rules:

- ðŸ“ **GitHub Repos** â†’ code quality, structure, frequency
- ðŸ§‘â€ðŸ’» **Commits** â†’ consistency, activity, skills shown
- ðŸ’¼ **LinkedIn** â†’ job titles, descriptions, keywords (via Exa)
- ðŸŽ¯ **Job Fit** â†’ match with required skills & experience
- ðŸ§  **AI Reasoning** â†’ Final combined judgment with score

